
Overview of verb please

The verb please has 3 senses (first 2 from tagged texts)
                                         
1. (15) please, delight -- (give pleasure to or be pleasing to; "These colors please the senses"; "a pleasing sensation")
2. (10) please -- (be the will of or have the will (to); "he could do many things if he pleased")
3. please -- (give satisfaction; "The waiters around her aim to please")

